Module atu.software
Package ie.atu.sw.model

Record Class ModuleInfo

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
ie.atu.sw.model.ModuleInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public record ModuleInfo(String moduleCode, String moduleTitle, int registrations, String programCode, String programTitle, int year, String school, String department, Examiner internalExaminer, Examiner externalExaminer) extends Record implements Serializable
A record representing information about a module. This record holds various attributes of a module, including code, title, registration numbers, associated program information, and assigned internal and external examiners.
